text: Thanasi Kokkinakis and Denis Kudla were the defending champions, but they did not participate this year. Johan Brunström and Nicholas Monroe won the title by defeating Sekou Bangoura and Frank Dancevic in the final by a score of 4–6, 6–3, [10–8]. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==External links== * Main Draw Nielsen Pro Tennis Championships - Doubles 2015 Doubles
